{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"671d2c7805","title":"邱会作对新疆军区党委及建设兵团党委的三点指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a33352f413","index":0,"year":1968,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"671d2c7805","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"邱会作","id":"4c92fd5264","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"边境地区和少数民族","id":"c0cd6cf1d4","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"a9e5101473","name":"邱会作"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"247d1d8734","type":"title","text":"邱会作对新疆军区党委及建设兵团党委的三点指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"671d2c7805","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e27346ba7","type":"paragraph","text":"〖这是元月二十七日邱会作部长在王恩茂和张希钦作完第二次检查后，对新疆军区党委、兵团党委、7335部队党委所作的指示。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"671d2c7805","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ef0a770e4","type":"paragraph","text":"目前最重要的是贯彻执行毛主席革命路线要忠于毛主席，要使毛主席革命路线在新疆贯彻下去：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"671d2c7805","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb38dabd36","type":"paragraph","text":"一、认真地检讨，按林副主席指示，要在灵魂深处爆发革命，错了就改，改了就好了，保是保不住的。（越保越坏，越保越垮台）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"671d2c7805","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b64974878e","type":"paragraph","text":"二、打倒派性，派性是毒蛇，是大联合的凶恶敌人。（是文化大革命的凶恶敌人）","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"671d2c7805","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab3787c71a","type":"paragraph","text":"三、要用最敏锐的思想，在新疆要搞大联合，大联合是根本的方向，要拼死拼活地去抓。（大联合是文化大革命的利益，是中国人民的根本利益，是世界人民的根本利益）","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"671d2c7805","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a434aca4ab","type":"paragraph","text":"（注）上面讲话材料摘录自新疆红二司政宣部办公室","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"671d2c7805","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40f05edf9b","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六八年二月七日《关于拼死拼活狠抓大联合工作的通知》","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"671d2c7805","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}